title: PES 3 [Repack by Tecnolog]
description:
Pro Evolution Soccer 3 (also known as Winning Eleven 7 in Japan and World Soccer Winning Eleven 7 in the US) is the third installment of Konami's Pro Evolution Soccer football video game series.

New graphics engine.
Improved gameplay, control, ball physics, animation and AI.
New Shop mode, where points can be traded in for hidden items.
Master League expanded to four divisions, with tons of new players.
For 1-4 players (multitap required for 3 or 4 players).

Developer(s)	Konami Computer Entertainment Tokyo
Publisher(s)	Konami
Composer(s)	Norikazu Miura
Series	Pro Evolution Soccer
Mode(s)	Single-player, Multiplayer
